 body cores. This region is likely too hot to either favor amino acid\nsynthesis or for amino acids to be retained after synthesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2014 21:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
