torial theory is obtained that is free of the\nabove mentioned pathologies. These techniques are applicable to general affine\nfield theories and Abelian gauge theories. The resulting quantized theory is\nshown to be dynamically local.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2014 10:44:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Mar 2014 13:44:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Sep 2014 11:59:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-24"}
